Package: dtaudit
Title: Audit and Diagnostic Tools for Data Analysis Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Fernando", "Meireles", , "fernando.meireles@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for auditing data analysis workflows, particularly those
    using data.table. Provides functions to validate join operations, compare
    data.tables, filter with diagnostic output, summarize data quality, clean
    variable and firm names, and export results to Excel. Designed to help
    analysts understand and document data transformations.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    data.table,
    stringi
Suggests:
    fixest,
    modelsummary,
    openxlsx,
    pbapply,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
